title: DAC7578 Breakout Side Connector Close-Up
summary: Low-angle close-up emphasizing one JST-SH connector on the DAC7578 breakout board. The board edge thickness and through-hole pads are visible.

structured_data.description: Front edge close-up photo of the PCB with the near STEMMA QT connector in focus and the opposite connector blurred in the background. Through-hole pin pads and edge mounting hole plating are visible.
